Author: missalligator
Text: So someone posted that picture of their arm to MPA saying “is this what you really want?” but I think the picture was really small so someone said “expand arm” as in make the picture bigger and people started joking about it like the Skins Cassie meme with the extra long arm that says “I expand arm till they take me to the hospital”. Whenever someone would ask for “tips and tricks” there were at least a few “expand arm” responses.
